data.description: A great opportunity to own a little piece of country, in the small community of Guinda.  This 0.99 acre property includes 2 separate units, the main home offers 3 spacious bedrooms, 1 bathroom and large livingroom. Second home is a 1 bedroom, 1 bath. Perfect for family or to rent for additional income.  The large lot has enough space to garden, park RV/boat, so many possibilities.  Come out a see for yourself.
